MERGE INTO dim_client AS tgt 
USING 
	(SELECT -1 AS client_key, 'Not Provided' AS client_pid, 'Not Provided' AS client_name, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS created_at, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS updated_at, 'SEED DATA' AS source_system)  AS src
ON tgt.client_pid = src.client_pid AND tgt.source_system = src.source_system
WHEN MATCHED THEN
	UPDATE SET client_key = src.client_key, client_name = src.client_name, updated_at = src.updated_at,source_system = src.source_system
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
	INSERT (client_key, client_pid, client_name, created_at, updated_at,  source_system) VALUES (src.client_key, src.client_pid, src.client_name, src.created_at, src.updated_at, src.source_system);

MERGE INTO  dim_sub_client AS tgt 
USING 
	(SELECT -1 AS sub_client_key, 'Not Provided' AS sub_client_pid, 'Not Provided' AS sub_client_name, -1 AS client_key, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS created_at, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS updated_at, 'SEED DATA' AS source_system)  AS src
ON tgt.sub_client_pid = src.sub_client_pid AND tgt.source_system = src.source_system
WHEN MATCHED THEN
	UPDATE SET sub_client_key = src.sub_client_key, sub_client_name = src.sub_client_name, client_key = src.client_key, updated_at = src.updated_at, source_system = src.source_system
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
	INSERT (sub_client_key, sub_client_pid, sub_client_name, client_key, created_at,
		updated_at, source_system) VALUES (src.sub_client_key, src.sub_client_pid, src.sub_client_name, src.client_key, src.created_at, src.updated_at, src.source_system);

MERGE INTO  dim_offering AS tgt 
USING 
	(
	SELECT	-1 AS offering_key, 'Not Provided' AS offering_pid, 'Not Provided' AS offering_name, 'Not Provided' AS offering_description,  -1 AS offering_type_key,      CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS created_at, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS updated_at, NULL AS deleted_at, 'SEED DATA' AS source_system)  AS src
ON tgt.offering_pid = src.offering_pid AND tgt.source_system = src.source_system
WHEN MATCHED THEN
	UPDATE SET offering_key= src.offering_key, offering_name = src.offering_name, offering_description = src.offering_description,  offering_type_key = src.offering_type_key, updated_at = src.updated_at, source_system = src.source_system
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
	INSERT (offering_key,offering_pid, offering_name,  offering_description,   offering_type_key,    created_at, updated_at, source_system) 
	VALUES (src.offering_key,src.offering_pid, src.offering_name,  src.offering_description,   src.offering_type_key,    src.created_at, src.updated_at, src.source_system) ;
